definitions.definition: A town and civil parish with a town council in Buckinghamshire , England , previously in Aylesbury Vale district ( OS grid ref SP8113 ) .
A village in the Rural Municipality of Craik , No. 222, Saskatchewan , Canada .
A rural locality in Canterbury , New Zealand .
